  "notes": "Ladin. Rhaeto-Romance language of the Dolomites (South Tyrol, Trentino, Belluno). ~30,000 speakers. Key features: (1) CA- → [tʃ] palatalisation. (2) Front rounded vowels /y, ø/. (3) Preservation of Latin PL-, CL-, FL- clusters. (4) Central vowel /ə/ in some varieties. German and Italian adstrate influence (Craffonara 1977).",
